snippet.title: Dungeon Drafters - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Manalith Studios combines mystery dungeon adventure with card battling in Dungeon Drafters. The newest trailer includes a deep dive showcase of how the game finds a happy marriage between these genres, along with the tools players will have their disposal to create their own playstyle.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
